OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,FFlights from Doncaster Sheffield
OL,7,FAirport wound down after the owners
OL,8,Fsaid the business was no longer viable.
OL,10,FDespite a campaign by politicians, the
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire metro mayor Oliver
OL,12,FCoppard and residents, Peel Group
OL,13,Fpressed ahead with plans to close the
OL,14,Fairport following a strategic review
OL,15,Fin 2022.
OL,17,FOperators Tui and Wizz Air have
OL,18,Falready started shifting scheduled
OL,19,Fservices to Leeds Bradford Airport.
