OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,FThe airport's operations will
OL,7,Fgradually be phased out in the coming
OL,8,Fdays.
OL,10,FWhen was the final flight?
OL,12,Fon Friday evening, 28 October 2022.
OL,14,FWizz Air's final flights, to Eastern
OL,15,FEurope, took off on 30 October.
OL,17,FThe company's last inbound service was
OL,18,Fa flight from Hurghada, Egypt,
OL,19,Farriving at 9.15pm on Friday, 4
OL,20,FNovember.
