OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,FThe final commercial service was a the
OL,7,FTui "positioning flight" to Manchester
OL,8,F` for passengers catching a plane on
OL,9,Fto another destination ` at 12.15am on
OL,10,F5 November 2022.
OL,12,FThe terminal remained available for
OL,13,Fpassenger services until 7am on the
OL,14,Fsame day, after which it closed.
OL,16,FWhy did the airport close?
OL,18,FDSA opened in 2005 after it was
OL,19,Fconverted by the Peel Group from the
OL,20,Fold RAF Finningley airbase.
