OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,FAt its peak it processed more than a
OL,7,Fmillion passengers a year, flying to
OL,8,F50 destinations.
OL,10,FBefore the Covid-19 pandemic, DSA was
OL,11,Fvoted the UK's best airport by Which?
OL,12,Fmagazine three years in a row.
OL,14,FIn a statement in July 2022 Peel Group
OL,15,Fsaid that DSA had never achieved a
OL,16,F"critical mass" of passengers to
OL,17,Fbecome profitable and this
OL,18,F"fundamental issue of a shortfall in
OL,19,Fpassenger numbers" was exacerbated by
OL,20,Fthe announcement Wizz Air would no
OL,21,Flonger use it as a permanent base.
