OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,FThe firm said the "challenge has been
OL,7,Fincreased by other changes in the
OL,8,Faviation market, the well-publicised
OL,9,Fimpact of the Covid-19 pandemic and
OL,10,Fincreasingly important environmental
OL,11,Fconsiderations".
OL,13,FIn September the same year, chairman
OL,14,Fof Peel Airports Group Robert Hough
OL,15,Fsaid: "The intractable problem remains
OL,16,Fthe fundamental and insufficient lack
OL,17,Fof current or prospective revenue
OL,18,Fstreams, together with the airport's
OL,19,Fhigh operating costs."
