OL,3,CWhy did Doncaster Sheffield Airport
OL,4,Cclose?
OL,6,Fto keep the airport running for
OL,7,Fanother year to allow time for a buyer
OL,8,Fto be found, saying it would only
OL,9,F"postpone the inevitable".
OL,11,FThe closure affected around 800
OL,12,Fworkers directly and hundreds more in
OL,13,Fthe supply chain.
OL,15,FSarah Barnes, of the GMB union, said
OL,16,Fat the time: "When the final flight
OL,17,Fleaves on Bonfire Night, hundreds if
OL,18,Fnot thousands of people will see their
OL,19,Ffuture go up in smoke.
