OL,6,F"GMB members are furious, the people
OL,7,Fof South Yorkshire can't allow it to
OL,8,Fhappen."
OL,10,FWhat are customers' rights if a flight
OL,11,Fis cancelled?
OL,13,FUnder UK law, if your flight is
OL,14,Fcancelled, your airline must let you
OL,15,Fchoose between a refund and an
OL,16,Falternative flight, no matter how far
OL,17,Fin advance of the scheduled departure
OL,18,Fdate the cancellation was made.
